{"type": "article", "id": 45502, "title": "这些气氛灯，像是森林中的神奇动物｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-24T23:01:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 44291, "name": "Ella & Pitr"}, {"id": 17108, "name": "Nikken Cutlery"}, {"id": 44292, "name": "Ebony Goh"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 148, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170924183214iPOM8gnohtFW6yf5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。</p><h3>Anim-Lamp by Flydesign</h3><p>虽然离圣诞节还有几个月的时间，不少家居品牌以及小型工作坊已经提前为营造气氛动起了脑筋。设计团队 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Flyconcept-1923203591284425\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flydesign</a> 想象了一个奇幻森林，将栖息在其中的神奇动物打造为木制气氛灯，看起来温润又可爱。Anim 采用触控式开关，允许人们尽情“戏弄”麋鹿的尾巴或是鸟儿的尖嘴。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/903848191/anim-lamp-imaginary-animal-shaped-lamp-for-home-an\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 69 澳元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183235KAdjbLMpEGZDoRez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183236vZeFKBtId0ElqbT1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.363235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183235sOFutYHnvw3RqW8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183236s1ydl4i85eqQzbfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183236iJBO1rZzsm65SMFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.492647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Great Katana Scissors by Nikken Cutlery</h3><p>位于日本岐阜县的关市曾经是著名的日本刀生产地，和平年代后主要生产工匠专用工具以及日用刀具。为了更好地推广锻刀文化，市政府与当地拥有 70 多年历史的刀具制造商 Nikken 共同推出了一套以名刀为原型的剪刀。他们还另外设计了迷你日本和室供人们展示，它不仅内置了 LED 灯，窗外的“景色”还可以更换成其它季节的风景照。目前推出的四款剪刀分别参考了织田信长、伊达政宗、坂本龙马以及德川家康的爱刀，如果你感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"https://nikkei.en-jine.com/projects/nikken-cutlery\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>订购，售价从 3800 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183303yaKF8pB6xwj0DTVP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665517\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183304AvgD46W0sXnMxpB9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562232\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183303LRcaNtlEQp68sUbj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183302mueGiVfnUTXJIpFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Felt Stone Rug by fluss design</h3><p>奥地利设计师 Martina Schuhmann 热衷于为地毯注入有趣的元素，她创立的 fluss design 专营看起来容易让人产生误解的“石制”家居。“石头”表面的纹路都是她用羊毛和丝绸等材质还原出的，内部则填充了乳胶海绵。你可以通过她的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/flussdesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店</a>购买到毛毯、抱枕以及小石头形状的装饰品，或是委托她进行定制。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183336a0sbNenFlxprvJyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750877\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183335GlqXUoZgVkbv4zLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749123\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092418333697ECf6nJRj1kGgSX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pinch by Ebony Goh</h3><p>买盐回家，是不是直接就把它们转移到调料罐里去了？悉尼设计师 <a href=\"http://ebonygoh.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ebony Goh</a> 为粗盐概念品牌 Pinch 设计的包装就这么直接放在厨房里好像也挺耐看的。像晶石一样充满棱角的透明包装直观地展现出三种风味粗盐的真实颜色，顶部像是标签一样的封条也采用了相当柔和的配色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183348LF7lwc5pzVonxIS1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183348X3ZScpPws5qLKJD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183351RbGjTZFozlBDSVIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755469\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Heads by Edwige Massart &amp; Xavier Wynn</h3><p>人体解剖图或是模型相信你一定没少看过，如果你那些真实的脏器替换成生活中那些乱七八糟的小物会如何？来自芝加哥的艺术家 Xavier Wynn 在参观当地博物馆时产生了一个改造解剖图的想法，于是便联手同为艺术家的妻子 Edwige Massart 开始创作名为 Heads 的雕塑系列。从四岁开始就有收藏小物习惯的 Massart 为这些“我头脑里的怪东西”贡献了自己的藏品，你可以通过他们的<a href=\"http://emnxw.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>看到全部作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183400ZDdA2XrCFhEwBoSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183401t8pMqYdchI0VgAC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183402JNOmhiCzBja52ygl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183402oB5nxLgpvEf37WOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Shipwreck of Bienvenu by Ella &amp; Pitr</h3><p>法国艺术家双人组合 <a href=\"http://www.ellapitr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ella &amp; Pitr</a> 自 2014 年开始热衷于根据周遭环境创作巨幅壁画，欧洲多个城市的房顶都留下了这对夫妇异想天开的创意。经常关注社会议题的他们以欧洲难民危机为主题带来了这幅名为 The Shipwreck of Bienvenu 的新作，这幅壁画位于法国圣埃蒂安市一个废弃的大坝上，描绘了一个正在休息的难民形象。身穿橙色救生衣的难民手拿着大坝的照片，像是在想象着到达法国后会发生什么。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183547VaW7ITwvMBh8kt1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183547WiTIUVmlNQK3jB7s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183547UzInld3DYCefx1BZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170924183548e2ZpUuhDcXf6qi3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}